    "description": "战斗。死亡。获胜！（可能多次死亡。） <br><br>《Next Up Hero》是一款地下城探索类游戏，主角是众多手绘英雄，通过砍砍杀杀、射击、手鼓、飞去来器和喷气机等方式，一路探索勇闯冒险。选择您的英雄（和/或邀请好友开启合作模式），开始扫荡地下城，全副武装，将属性提升到最高，对抗名为无休挽歌的邪恶怪物。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>击败了 Boss？<strong>为社区制作您自己的地下城</strong><br></li><li>地下城已击败？<strong>试试疯狂难度！</strong> <br></li><li>你试过了？<strong>那就最小-最大化您最喜爱的角色。</strong><br></li><li>已最大化所有英雄？<strong>到</strong>  <strong>上告诉我们您接下来想要什么！</strong><br></li><li>您真的全试过？<strong>跟您最喜爱的合作模式搭档再试一次。</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Next Up Hero》？那又如何？我有的是地下城探索者！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/f783efc8976b928956f48d727eb574ac.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/cc6cbcd646b997deda98a2349fe28459.poster.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/cc6cbcd646b997deda98a2349fe28459.webm?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/cc6cbcd646b997deda98a2349fe28459.mp4?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>幻想自己是个游戏设计师？让我们看看您的天份。制作一个残酷的地下城，挑战社区能否击败。如果他们击败地下城，就能保留一件稀有战利品。如果失败，宝物就是您的。 <br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/b3d0449eaba0344a05c2dcba5d9c2236.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/3cdf1a3d7ea9bed79e7e731e99623c51.poster.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/3cdf1a3d7ea9bed79e7e731e99623c51.webm?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/3cdf1a3d7ea9bed79e7e731e99623c51.mp4?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《Next Up Hero》中，死亡是永久性的，您的“回音”会留下，供下一位玩家召唤。大家在《Next Up Hero》中死亡次数很多，因此您最多可以复活 20 个 AI 随从！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/c9c97140da327bb8849e464f9182c604.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/ff5e72689e6ece3dd7fd239cef3b7441.poster.avif?t=1674673929\" width=616 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/ff5e72689e6ece3dd7fd239cef3b7441.webm?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667810/extras/ff5e72689e6ece3dd7fd239cef3b7441.mp4?t=1674673929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这是 Mixer Interactive 授权的英雄与挽歌之战。旁观者可以控制回音军队，帮助英雄在楼层中存活，或强化挽歌敌人，减速和冰冻玩家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持的游戏手柄</h2>Microsoft® Xbox® 360 Controller for Windows® (Wired)<br>Microsoft® Xbox® One Controller (Wired)<br>Microsoft® Xbox® One Elite Controller<br>SONY® PS4 DUALSHOCK®4 wireless controller (Wired)<br>Logitech RumblePad™ 2<br>Logitech™ Dual Action™<br>Logitech™ Wireless Gamepad F710<br>Logitech™ Gamepad F310<br>Afterglow Wired Controller for Xbox 360<br>Rock Candy Controller for Xbox 360<br>Thrustmaster GPX Controller for Xbox 360<br>RAZER Sabertooth",
